# Gridspace Guava Python SDK

You will need two environment variables to use the SDK.

```bash
export GUAVA_API_KEY="..."
export GUAVA_AGENT_NUMBER="..."
```

You can also optionally use your own OpenAI key
```bash
export OPENAI_API_KEY="..."
```

Once those environment variables are set, you can run the examples.

```bash
uv run python -m guava.examples.property_insurance +15556667777
```

or e.g.
```bash
uv run python -m guava.examples.guava.thai_palace
```